  "title": "Playful Spanish Rice Krispies Paella",
  "description": "A kid-friendly Spanish dish featuring Rice Krispies, this paella is a fun twist on traditional recipes, incorporating ayurvedic-rajasic-friendly ingredients in a hot pot vessel. It's perfect for a family dinner or snack.",
